description:
This session will highlight how Splunk uses Jenkins to provide an end-to-end solution in the development CI system. Attendees will see how test results are delivered to a Splunk indexer, where they can be analyzed and presented in a variety of ways. This session will also include a live demonstration.

Delivered by Bill Houston and Ali Raza
title: Jenkins World 2016 - Jenkins at Splunk and Splunking Jenkins
